<h3>Dear Buyer</h3>

<p>
    The Share Purchase Agreement (SPA) for your purchase has been uploaded to the interest you made. Please read and confirm the SPA, so that the sale can be concluded.
</p>

<p>
    <%= render "/secondary_sale_mailer/sale", secondary_sale: @secondary_sale, current_user: nil %>
</p>

<p class="btn btn-primary"><%= link_to 'View Sale & Accept SPA', secondary_sale_url(@secondary_sale, tab: "offerings-tab", subdomain: @secondary_sale.entity.sub_domain) %></p>

<h3>Next Steps</h3>
<p>
    <ul>
        <li>Login and check details of your offer.</li>
        <li>Read the SPA attached to your offer.</li>
        <li>Accept the SPA.</li>
    </ul>
</p>

